Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.69,0:10:10.39,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\}Azu-nyan!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.83,0:16:42.17,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\}Chị đừng cố kéo cái chậu vào nữa!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.17,0:16:43.49,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\}Tiếp theo là gì nhỉ?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.49,0:16:44.10,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\}Cảnh uống trà.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.55,0:16:48.88,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\}Loại đắt tiền à?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.05,0:17:34.46,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\}Ăn đàng hoàng đi!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.66,0:17:37.11,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\}Để được ăn nhiều hơn...
